<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.279413>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Type material of the Tortricidae described by Fabricius. A: Pyralis abbreviana, B: P. abietana, C: P. abildgaardana, D: P. boscana, E: P. laterana, F: P. lundana, G: P. m i x t a n a, H: P. pflugiana, I: Tinea compositella, J: P. daldorfana, K: P. schumacherana, L: P. ro b o r a n a, M: P. bipunctana, N: P. trapezana, O: P. reticulana, P: P. asperana, Q: P. isertana, R: P. rivellana, S: P. dorsana, T: P. strigana. Scale bars = 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/279413/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.279414>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Original labels of the Tortricidae described by Fabricius. A: Pyralis abbreviana, B: P. abietana, C: P. abildgaardana, D: P. boscana, E: P. laterana, F: P. lundana, G: P. m i x t a n a, H: P. pflugiana, I: Tinea compositella, J: P. daldorfana, K: P. schumacherana, L: P. ro b o r a n a, M: P. bipunctana, N: P. trapezana, O: P. reticulana, P: P. asperana, Q: P. isertana, R: P. rivellana, S: P. dorsana, T: P. strigana." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/279414/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

